%
% Final mesh refinement using MMG. Size of the elements depends on the distance to the fault plane
%

****mesher
 ***mesh mesh_remeshed.geo
  **open mesh_before_remeshing.geo
  **adaptation
   *min_size .0005
   *max_size .05
   *verbose   6
   *metric from_file file metric_mmg.dat
   *volume_mesher mmg3d
    hgrad 1.25
    hausd 0.01

   *preserve_elsets

    ASTHENOSPHERE-1-OCEANIC
    ASTHENOSPHERE-1-CONTINENTAL
    ASTHENOSPHERE-2-OCEANIC
    ASTHENOSPHERE-2-CONTINENTAL
    AW
    OCEAN
    CH-0-70
    CH-70-200
    CH-200-270
    CH-270-670
    LITHOSPHERE_CONTINENTAL
    LITHOSPHERE_OCEANIC
    UPPER-MANTLE
    LOWER-MANTLE
    SLAB
    SLAB-0-200
    SLAB-200-270
    SLAB-270-BOTTOM
    LAYER-54-70-OCEANIC

   *preserve_bsets
    fault_plane

****return
